hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nclose專欄都無<br />\n<br />\n仲去泛民主場新聞開多個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2fbbaa10d419cf31d42c413a3b37568585377be","tid":197703,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T16:20:30.000Z","msg":"云伯最新UPDATE<br />\n難道見完共匪有靈感?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/wan.chin.75/posts/10155034109047225\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwan.chin.75%2Fposts%2F10155034109047225&d=0xR7vGHOl893LUq1yoppejCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=149cbe02\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/wan.chin.75/posts/10155034109047225</a><br />\n<br />\nWan Chin <br />\n2017年3月17日 12:57 <br />\n<br />\n陳雲： <br />\n<br />\n這段時間，我忙於寫書，但也盡了最大的善意，與幾批南下的黨官，談香港特首選舉和新一屆特首的施政，以便習近平總書記七月來香港的時候，留一點顏面給他老人家。"},{"pid":"3abf37e9ffcf8d16318772212f5c6e3c354e91c2","tid":197703,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T16:23:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>云伯最新UPDATE<br />\n難道見完共匪有靈感?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/wan.chin.75/posts/10155034109047225\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwan.chin.75%2Fposts%2F10155034109047225&d=0xR7vGHOl893LUq1yoppejCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=149cbe02\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/wan.chin.75/posts/10155034109047225</a><br />\n<br />\nWan Chin <br />\n2017年3月17日 12:57 <br />\n<br />\n陳雲： <br />\n<br />\n這段時間，我忙於寫書，但也盡了最大的善意，與幾批南下的黨官，談香港特首選舉和新一屆特首的施政，以便習近平總書記七月來香港的時候，留一點顏面給他老人家。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>4日後又話唔寫, 條友開始忽忽地</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/wan.chin.75/posts/10155045389307225\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwan.chin.75%2Fposts%2F10155045389307225&d=0xR7vGHOl893LUq1yoppejCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=64cea9e8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/wan.chin.75/posts/10155045389307225</a><br />\n<br />\nWan Chin<br />\n3月21日 11:21 &middot; <br />\n<br />\n原先打算在書展推出《華夏邦聯論》，看來也是免了。為他人作嫁衣裳，沒意思。還是給特朗普總統示範吧，陳雲在香港為他敲鑼打鼓好了。心情很差，我打算擱下《華夏邦聯論》不寫，改寫一本歌頌特朗普總統的書。"},{"pid":"37741941fb12a915de037b8a17adc94839bfff82","tid":197703,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T16:31:19.000Z","msg":"云伯江郎才盡, 只能炒冷飯<br />\n仲賣HK$148 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/wan.chin.75/posts/10155113886982225\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwan.chin.75%2Fposts%2F10155113886982225&d=0xR7vGHOl893LUq1yoppejCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=4ef3ec2b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/wan.chin.75/posts/10155113886982225</a><br />\nWan Chin <br />\n4月12日 12:42 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s23.postimg.org/kq0ucrip7/image.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs23.postimg.org%2Fkq0ucrip7%2Fimage.jpg&h=9b53f432&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n乜鬼都炒埋一碟<br />\n<br />\n大中華膠力甚強<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ea7e76c945b9aa64bd96c786a033e5799520f7e","tid":197703,"uid":67813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T17:36:35.000Z","msg":"有咩人會買"},{"pid":"af9ee75193df5bf4e4afd90a9e8732edbcef11dd","tid":197703,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T18:53:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有咩人會買</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n仲會諗住結乜春華夏邦聯, 與支那一齊對抗美帝既人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://oi68.tinypic.com/2hxq5bl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Foi68.tinypic.com%2F2hxq5bl.jpg&h=f395c5f2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b69e2b47affe2fcad9e4c80cf6d800925f142724","tid":197703,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T04:29:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>佢話退Facebook夠無退啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n云伯講咁多野, 有邊樣係真係做到架?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同中共deal 就係真<br />\n<br />\n不過因為佢廢 完成唔到任務, 所以入政府做官 or 去支那大學教書.....一樣野都冇</blockquote><br />\n佢成功搞散本土派啦，不過共匪走佢數咋嘛棄卒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"975a213ad90b9c5765b68499009e4e416b8d3a8a","tid":197703,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T00:45:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ec855edcd3130fc434e2e466d02ecb89bacf7428","tid":197703,"uid":27991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T02:14:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>叫葉政淳幫佢寫咪得😂</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n作者簡介係咪寫：「尖沙咀商廈看更, 半夜無野做時所寫」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n邊座商廈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a67e384ce9bf783b7281ddbee6b33de6f006e48","tid":197703,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T02:17:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>佢話退Facebook夠無退啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgm